Purdue University North Central teams are members of [[National Association of Intercollegiate Athletics|NAIA]] and compete within the [[Chicagoland Collegiate Athletic Conference]]. Intercollegiately, Purdue University North Central sponsors a men's basketball team, a men's baseball team, a women's volleyball team, and a women's [[softball]] team. The moniker of Purdue University North Central's teams is the Panther Boilers. The official mascot is Pounce, the Panther Boiler.
